        {
          "type": "text",
          "size": "t",
          "text": [
            "This project started with me looking outside my window at a few workers on scaffolding. There was something about the perspective and fluidity of their work that caught my eye. I wanted to bring focus onto the hundreds of workers who create these massive monuments that we live in and take for granted."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "size": "t",
          "text": [
            "The idea was to accumulate their motion, revealing the building as they go, ensuring that their work left a mark."
          ]
        },
